        <mxCell id="KX4MmI35KY4r6R5Pd4ZA-20" parent="KX4MmI35KY4r6R5Pd4ZA-23" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;hachureGap=4;fontFamily=Mali;strokeWidth=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#666666;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;labelBorderColor=none;textShadow=0;labelBackgroundColor=none;align=left;spacing=7;verticalAlign=middle;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DMali;" value="&lt;div&gt;The model learns from the labeled data first, then uses its own predictions&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(pseudo-labels) or consistency rules on unlabeled data to improve itself iteratively.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
