        <mxCell id="5cy4-kSeaGVhRb9U9V7c-12" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;fontFamily=Mali;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;spacingLeft=5;rounded=1;arcSize=9;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DMali;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;`Y`: Dependent variable (what you want to predict)&lt;br&gt;`X_n`: independent variables&lt;br&gt;`\beta_0`: Intercept (value of `Y` when `X=0`)&lt;br&gt;`\beta_1`: Slope (change in `Y` for a one-unit change in `X`)&lt;br&gt;`\epsilon`: Error term&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
